{"tid":1156683,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[眾籌] 我諗住買個headset，用嚟打機用，希望大家支持下","createTime":"2019-05-15T18:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T15:24:16.000Z","uid":54451,"like":38,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"401fb31ccca7286fcb900a024f96cbd37b9641e2","tid":1156683,"uid":54451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"見隔離post借時事話題拍條片要籌600k，籌得咁爽我又籌下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />目標係800k<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1156244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1156244</a><br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n<br />\n首先點都要戴個頭盔先，大家好，今次我係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em>借連登呢個平台嚟cap水嘅</em></span>，反正免費<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>背景</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n驚自爆唔答<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>點解要咁做？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nCap你地水，如果你地有閒錢剩嘅可以捐俾我，我絕對冇逼你地㗎<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>點解咁貴？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n小弟諗住買貴少少，想用外國名牌headset，headset嘅質素就好重要，一分錢，一分貨。<br />\n有錢剩就拎嚟自己用，反正你班水魚唔知我拎去點用，走數都冇人知啦。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>可以點幫到手？</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n第一，入錢落我互口<br />\n<br />\n第二，幫到人手之餘仲可以做善事，1 rock 2 birds<br />\n<br />\n第三，如果我cap完水冇買靚headset嘅，希望你哋唔好屌住，等到個Headset到咗，我出review睇得出質素好差先屌<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持，多謝！"},{"pid":"c7b0a77c25e36bf5c29366856647546ed73cb8e9","tid":1156683,"uid":54451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WkHpS8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WkHpS8.png&h=b4f6a862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我有冇買你哋到時就知㗎啦！"},{"pid":"d349def9313653e63b773f34fa14c79007471056","tid":1156683,"uid":63124,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:31:48.000Z","msg":"愛心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"9bc896286d5dc0c728dc37799adc3d50cef2bbbf","tid":1156683,"uid":149329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:33:05.000Z","msg":"心水ching"},{"pid":"704fe284290d109b856ac5324b